The paper proposes a novel learning framework using recurrent neural networks for solving inverse problems in image reconstruction tasks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and information theory (cs.IT).
